00:46:10.110 --> 00:46:12.840
$10 a shot to see it.

00:46:12.840 --> 00:46:14.180
It's possible.

00:46:14.180 --> 00:46:18.900
So basically, almost always,
inequalities will be greater

00:46:18.900 --> 00:46:21.020
than or equal to, or less than
or equal to in this course.

00:46:21.020 --> 00:46:23.250
It's more fun to talk about
the not equal to case, the

00:46:23.250 --> 00:46:24.180
non-linear case.

00:46:24.180 --> 00:46:26.290
But linear cases will
